message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Cloud-Assisted Obstacle-Overtaking Simulator"
abstract: >-
  Microscopic traffic simulator (IDM-based) for a one-lane two-way road with a
  localized obstacle, comparing a centralized cloud-based slot-reservation
  coordinator against a decentralized one-lane-bridge baseline. Reproduces all
  figures and tables of the associated AVEC'26 / IJAE paper.
